# ============================================================================
# Project Specific - Keep These Files
# ============================================================================
# Keep important configuration and documentation
!README.md
!QUICKSTART.md
!PROJECTSUMMARY.md
!WINDOWSSETUP.md
!requirements.txt
!setup.py
!config.py
